@28000 = ~Alright, you two, listen up. This here's a moment for you both to learn, to grow, and to prove yourselves.~
@28001 = ~Khalid, you've got the experience, the wisdom. Share it, but don't hold back. And you, newcomer, show us what you're made of.~
@28002 = ~This ain't about putting on a spectacle. It's about grit, about technique. Remember, this is your chance to step up. Now, let's see who's got the fire inside.~
@28003 = ~Begin!~
@28004 = ~Well, well, looks like we've got a surprise on our hands, don't we? In this corner, our newcomer has shown us a thing or two about determination and skill.~
@28005 = ~Khalid, you fought well, no doubt about that. But today, victory belongs to the fresh blood. You've earned your keep, mate.~
@28006 = ~Here's your share of the purse, a testament to your prowess. Wear it as a badge of honor. This won't be the last time we see you in these pits, I reckon. Well done.~
@28007 = ~Alright, you two. This is what you've been training for. Grom, I see the fire in your eyes. Remember, this ain't about drawing blood. It's about testing your limits, honing your skills. No lethal blows.~
@28008 = ~And you, newcomer. You've got something to prove here. Grom's a different beast altogether. He'll test your mettle in ways you haven't seen yet. Adapt and fight smart. It's a whole new game.~
@28009 = ~Show us what you're made of!~
@28010 = ~Well, I'll be damned. You did it, <CHARNAME>. You faced Grom and came out on top. That's no small feat. You've got real potential, I'll give you that.~
@28011 = ~Take your winnings, and remember, this is just the beginning. There's more to come, and I've no doubt you'll face it head-on. Well done.~
@28012 = ~Ladies and gentlemen, welcome back to the pits! Today, we have an exciting match for you.~
@28013 = ~In one corner, we have our seasoned rogue, Lyria 'Frostbite' Winterheart, known for her quick strikes and evasive moves.~
@28014 = ~And in the other corner, our new contender, <CHARNAME>, climbing the ranks and eager to make a name for <HIMHER>self.~
@28015 = ~Let the match begin!~
@28016 = ~Well now, that was a bout to remember! You've got a spark in you, <CHARNAME>. Took on Lyria like a seasoned fighter.~
@28017 = ~This arena's seen its share of battles, but a victory like yours, unexpected and hard-fought, it's what makes this place special.~
@28018 = ~Here's your cut, well earned. Keep this up, and you'll be etching your name in the annals of the pits history.~
@28019 = ~Bear witness, for we have a match of extraordinary promise before us today.~
@28020 = ~Our new challenger, with valor in their eyes, faces none other than Serra Swiftwind, the archer of Silverymoon.~
@28021 = ~Serra stands proud and tall with her bow poised and her spirit attuned to nature's grace. Strength and skill will surely intertwine in this dance of combat!~
@28022 = ~Now, let the clash begin!~
@28023 = ~Well fought, well fought indeed! Our challenger has proven themselves once again, overcoming formidable odds!~
@28024 = ~Serra Swiftwind, your grace and precision with the bow are unmatched. And yet, it seems today, our newcomer's determination shone brighter. A testament to the unpredictable nature of the pits.~
@28025 = ~Here stands a testament to courage and tenacity. A share of the earnings for this display of skill and willpower.~
@28026 = ~Remember, friends, the pits have their own rhythm, and today, it played in favor of our challenger. Let this victory inspire us all to greater heights!~
@28027 = ~Ladies and gentlemen, gather 'round! Today, we have a match that will be etched in the annals of this arena's history! A clash of titans, a contest of wills!~
@28028 = ~In this corner, we have the current champion, a living legend, Roran 'Iron Fist' Stonebreaker! His fists are like thunder, his strikes like lightning!~
@28029 = ~And in this corner, <CHARNAME>, who's fought tooth and nail to reach this moment, a newcomer who's faced formidable foes and triumphed!~
@28030 = ~It's time to see if they've got what it takes to dethrone the champion!~
@28031 = ~Let the battle begin!~
@28032 = ~What a match we have just witnessed! <CHARNAME>, against all odds, has emerged victorious against the reigning champion!~
@28033 = ~A feat that will be sung about in the taverns and spoken of in hushed tones for ages to come!~
@28034 = ~This is what the pits are about, my friends! A testament to the indomitable spirit, to the unyielding will to fight! This is where legends are born and stories are forged!~
@28035 = ~You have shown us all the true heart of a warrior. You faced the best and emerged victorious.~
@28036 = ~You have earned not only the title of champion, but the respect and admiration of everyone here.~
@28037 = ~Your winnings, well-earned and rightfully deserved. Wear them with pride, for you have proven yourself in the crucible of combat!~
@28038 = ~Ladies and gentlemen, warriors and spectators, today is a day that will be remembered for ages to come. We have a special surprise for you all.~
@28039 = ~After a prolonged absence, a true legend has returned to grace our arena. Isla Darkcloak has emerged from retirement to face our current champion in a DEATHMATCH!~
@28040 = ~This is a rare and monumental event, a clash of champions that promises to leave an indelible mark on the history of the pits.~
@28041 = ~Now, without further ado, let the battle of the ages commence!~
@28042 = ~The fight is over! As the dust settles and the echoes of battle fade, history is made in the pits today!~
@28043 = ~<CHARNAME> has emerged victorious, claiming a place of honor among the legends of combat. Isla Darkcloak fought with unyielding spirit, as did our reigning champion.~
@28044 = ~Yet, it was <CHARNAME> who proved themselves worthy of this moment. Their skill and determination will be remembered for ages to come.~
@28045 = ~Let us pay tribute to both warriors for their valor. Now, we crown a new champion, one who has faced the fiercest trials and emerged triumphant.~
@28046 = ~Champion, take your place in the annals of pit-fighting glory!~
